&lt;h4 id="scoped-access-control">Scoped Access Control&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>Each ServiceAccount can be granted fine-grained access using &lt;strong>RBAC&lt;/strong> policies, limiting what it can read, modify, or list in the cluster.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>